| Cumulative ERA5 rainfall, domain mean | ~$cum_rain_mm mm over the $window_days-d window |
| GloFAS peak Q on the main reach | $glofas_peak_q m³/s |

> **Important caveat**: rain-on-grid only. If the event was driven by
> upstream discharge or barrier failure, the modelled extent is **not**
> directly EMS-comparable. The animation is best read as a
> terrain + low-lying-area exposure visualisation with the EMS polygons
> overlaid as ground truth.

